 * "Re: "Obsessed With the Hunt," by Susan Estrich, Opinion, March 27: 
</P>
<P>
 Ms. Estrich just doesn't get it. Whitewater and Watergate have a lot more in 
common than water. Both concern primarily questions concerning the character, 
trust and ethics of a sitting President (and in Whitewater an unelected but 
very active spouse and her former law and business partners). 
</P>
<P>
 People are rightly judged by the company they keep. Let the facts come out. 
They will speak for themselves. 
</P>
<P>
 EUGENE P. CARVER 
