<P>
COLLEGE BASEBALL ROUNDUP; ZEICHICK'S INSIDE JOB PROPELS VALLEY RALLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jamie Zeichick hit an inside-the-park grand slam with two out in the ninth 
inning Thursday to highlight a six-run rally and lift Valley College to an 11-5 
Western State Conference baseball victory over Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Zeichick's line drive to left-center rolled to more than 400 feet from home 
plate for his fourth home run. 
</P>
<P>
 Jorge Dorado was four for four, including a pair of triples, for Valley 
(9-14-1, 7-7 in conference play). 
</P>
