<TEXT>
<P>
 Ex-Banker Sued Again: Former Orange County banker Ronald L. Rodgers is facing 
more legal problems, but he may not know it yet. 
</P>
<P>
 Rodgers, ousted last year from his position as president of Bank of Newport, 
was sued last week by Frontier Bank in La Palma for defaulting on a $130,000 
loan.But a lawyer for the bank said no one has been able to find the one-time 
banker to serve him with the lawsuit. 
</P>
<P>
