<TEXT>
<P>
 Trucking strike -- A story in Wednesday's editions on the nationwide trucking 
strike incorrectly reported that Quikway Trucking Co. is a non-union firm. The 
Los Angeles-based company in fact employs members of Teamsters Local 208. 
</P>
